						<summary>

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1303, Durmati, Rishabha, ba. 6, Wednesday, Aviṭṭam (A.D. 1381, May 15). and mentions <hi rend="bold">Kampaṇa-Uḍaiyar</hi> at about the end. This is much damaged and seems to record a remission of some taxes consequent on a draught and famine (?) in the country during the (previous) year Raudri. </p>						

						</summary>
